### Where it's slow

From `-Z time-passes`:

* `item_bodies_checking`

From [sample-head.txt](https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/files/10089082/sample-head.txt):

* `ExprUseVisitor` when [called by](https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/blob/ff8c8dfbe66701531e3e5e335c28c544d0fbc945/compiler/rustc_hir_typeck/src/upvar.rs#L203-L210) `rustc_hir_typeck::upvar::FnCtxt::analyze_closure`

